title: Noticed a slight style issue with the Bow charges, where the charge with the  *…
message: Noticed a slight style issue with the Bow charges, where the charge with the  * on it (ie the one added by Load Up) wasn't being bolded, but the one before it was. Also, the star was visible on the UI. Fixed the issue. Additionally, added support for bows with only three levels of charge (ie the Shalya Bow line), which may fix an issue when running on xtrestolite Lollipop.

title: Fixed the rapid/crouch fire section of the Light/Heavy Bowgun detail page to be…
message: Fixed the rapid/crouch fire section of the Light/Heavy Bowgun detail page to be higher and have the correct list of ammo types for rapid/crouch fire (ammo for those was stored in a column that wasn't being retrieved - that's been fixed). Also, if there is no rapid/crouch fire (see the LBG Cross Bowgun), no text will be displayed. Which is nice.
